    "eyebrow": "Introduction",
    "num": "01",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">01</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Introduction</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Welcome to Understanding the Term 'Texican'</h2><ul><li>Explore the meaning and origin of 'Texican'</li><li>Understand historical context in Mexican Texas</li><li>Engage in interactive activities to assess prior knowledge</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">This lesson begins by clarifying the term 'Texican,' tracing its origins and evolution within the historical context of Mexican Texas. We will engage learners with interactive activities to surface their prior knowledge and associations with related terms. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s6\">[6]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> An interactive poll will ask learners what they think 'Texican' means before revealing historical definitions.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Reflect on your current understanding of 'Texican' and related terms like 'Texian' and 'Texan'.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Confusing 'Texican' with 'Texian' or 'Texan' without considering historical and political context.</p></div></div>",
