    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">12</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Reflection</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Reflecting on 'Texican' Terminology</h2><ul><li>How has your understanding of 'Texican' changed?</li><li>What challenges did you encounter in distinguishing terms?</li><li>How will this knowledge influence your study of Texas history?</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Reflection encourages learners to consolidate their learning and consider implications for further study. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Learners might note initial confusion between 'Texican' and 'Texian' and now appreciate the political and cultural distinctions.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Write a brief reflection on your learning experience regarding 'Texican' terminology.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Skipping reflection and missing opportunities for deeper learning.</p></div></div>",
