    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">34</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Timeline Activity Introduction</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Tracing Texican Involvement in Key Events</h2><ul><li>Review major conflicts involving Texicans from Spanish rule to Texas Republic</li><li>Identify Texican roles in military and political developments</li><li>Prepare to create a detailed timeline of Texican history</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Understanding Texican history requires mapping their involvement across multiple conflicts and political changes, highlighting their evolving roles. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s8\">[8]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Plotting the 1821 Mexican independence as a turning point for Texican political engagement.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Begin listing key events where Texicans played significant roles.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Overlooking Texican contributions in early events before the Texas Revolution.</p></div></div>",
